OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774361471
OL,3,CTempers flare ahead of Tyne-Wear derby
OL,4,Cin Newcastle
OL,6,FThere is a huge police presence in
OL,7,FNewcastle city centre as football fans
OL,8,Fturned out ahead of the first Tyne-
OL,9,FWear men's derby in the city in a
OL,10,Fdecade.
OL,12,FPolice faced an enormous challenge of
OL,13,Fkeeping fans from Sunderland and
OL,14,FNewcastle apart as tensions rose ahead
OL,15,Fof the Premiership clash at St James'
OL,16,FPark.
OL,18,FOfficers lined in formation to
OL,19,Fseparate home and away fans, with
OL,20,Fmounted units and police dressed in
OL,21,Friot gear.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
