FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774361471
OL,3,CTempers flare ahead of Tyne-Wear derby
OL,4,Cin Newcastle
OL,6,FMeanwhile, on the pitch the game had
OL,7,Fto temporarily paused in the second
OL,8,Fhalf due to a report of discriminatory
OL,9,Fabuse directed at Sunderland player
OL,10,FLutsharel Geertruida.
OL,12,FThe incident will now be fully
OL,13,Finvestigated.
OL,15,FA statement published on the Premier
OL,16,FLeague's X account said: "The incident
OL,17,Fat St James' Park will now be fully
OL,18,Finvestigated. We offer our full
OL,19,Fsupport to the player and both clubs.
OL,20,FRacism has no place in our game, or
OL,21,Fanywhere in society.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774361471
OL,3,CTempers flare ahead of Tyne-Wear derby
OL,4,Cin Newcastle
OL,6,F"We will continue to work with
OL,7,Fstakeholders and authorities to ensure
OL,8,Four stadiums are an inclusive and
OL,9,Fwelcoming environment for all."
OL,11,FNorthumbria Police confirmed one
OL,12,Fperson had been arrested ahead of the
OL,13,F12pm kick-off.
OL,15,FA spokesperson said: "We are aware of
OL,16,Fa number of videos circulating on
OL,17,Fsocial media in relation to Newcastle
OL,18,FUnited and Sunderland supporters
OL,19,Fgoading one another.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774361471
OL,3,CTempers flare ahead of Tyne-Wear derby
OL,4,Cin Newcastle
OL,6,F"In the main, everyone has co-operated
OL,7,Fand we are able to report that one
OL,8,Farrest was made ahead of kick-off.
OL,10,F"We will continue to have an increased
OL,11,Fpolice presence in the city centre."
OL,13,FMore than 2,500 Sunderland fans
OL,14,Ftravelled to Tyneside and were
OL,15,Fescorted by police from Newcastle
OL,16,FCentral Station. Latecomers faced
OL,17,Fbeing guided through large groups of
OL,18,FNewcastle fans as they made their way
OL,19,Fin to the ground.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
