PN,42705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774361471
OL,3,CTempers flare ahead of Tyne-Wear derby
OL,4,Cin Newcastle
OL,6,FThe Sunderland team bus was damaged
OL,7,Fafter being pelted with bottles as it
OL,8,Farrived at the stadium, while fans
OL,9,Fwere also throwing flares. There are
OL,10,Fno reported injuries.
OL,12,FHours before the match, hundreds of
OL,13,Ffans were seen queueing outside city
OL,14,Fcentre venues, including Shearer's and
OL,15,FStack.
OL,17,FMore to follow.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
